&lt;p&gt;Every serious MarTech-, AdTech-, and Data- platform is now competing to build customer value in the agentic era of AI. While model capability is improving quickly, an AI agent is only as good as the cross-channel context it can reason over. Supermetrics provides that context: the governed, normalized marketing data and semantic layer that platforms can trust and build their own products on top of.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
